{"tid":2070662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議員蔣旻正：教協葉建源真的脫隊了","createTime":"2020-06-19T09:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T09:28:29.000Z","uid":70063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbdabd9fb08eeeb2d1e118f03d0af9ea10a51e2","tid":2070662,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"早前我公開邀請教協參加教育界初選，教協拒絕參加初選，拒絕作出攬炒承諾，但強調「教協一直是泛民一員，唔會脫隊」。（立場新聞連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3dcRuY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3dcRuY0&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=b4e5f0a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3dcRuY0</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n如今林鄭推張舉能任終審法院首席法官，張舉能法官曾經引釋法駁回梁頌恆、游蕙禎DQ。在立法會決議中，全體建制派護航支持，除了專業議政5名功能組別議員葉建源、李國麟、莫乃光、梁繼昌、郭榮鏗外，全體泛民、本土派議員均反對或棄權。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：何桂藍〈功能組別也要面對全香港人〉<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30Vmzx6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30Vmzx6&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=35064891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30Vmzx6</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會就委任張舉能為首席法官投票<br />\n<br />\n✅支持：<br />\n📌全體建制派議員<br />\n📌葉建源、李國麟、莫乃光、梁繼昌、郭榮鏗<br />\n<br />\n❎反對或棄權<br />\n梁耀忠、毛孟靜、朱凱廸、陳志全、鄭松泰、許智峯、鄺俊宇、黃碧雲、林卓廷、胡志偉、譚文豪、郭家麒、陳淑莊、楊岳橋、張超雄、邵家臻<br />\n<br />\n#立法會 #教協 #葉建源 #專業議政 #民主派 #泛民 #脫隊 #功能組別 #攬炒自救<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OHeZw3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOHeZw3V.jpg&h=1f9db316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chiangmanching/photos/a.103274661023835/278954633455836/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchiangmanching%2Fphotos%2Fa.103274661023835%2F278954633455836%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=aa94e8b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chiangmanching/photos/a.103274661023835/278954633455836/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"e06acd216220f44712db8258ad6943199438d82e","tid":2070662,